CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier reads:" Students Win American Legion Awards- Pennsylvania Railroad American Legion Post 500 presented awards for "Americanism" to Richard Gaither and Eleanor Davis, 8-A Letsche School students here Monday at promotion exercises. Cmdr. Edward W. Armstrong and Vice Cmdr. William W. Shaffer made the presentations."
TitMainTitle: Cmdr. Edward W. Armstrong and Vice Cmdr. William W. Shaffer presenting American Legion awards to Eleanor Davis and Richard Gaither, standing in Letche School with stage in background
